# ==========================================
# Trivy Exception Management (Demo Environment)
# ==========================================

# [Accepted Risk] EKS Control Plane Access
# Reason: Public access and CIDR (0.0.0.0/0) intentionally enabled strictly for local `kubectl` management during the development/demo phase.
# Mitigation: To be disabled in Production; access will be routed via Bastion Host or AWS Client VPN.
AWS-0040
AWS-0041

# [Deferred Implementation] RDS Identity Management
# Reason: Currently utilizing AWS Secrets Manager with boto3 for credential injection (12-Factor App compliant).
# Migration to full RDS IAM Authentication via IRSA is deferred to future phases.
AWS-0176

# [Operational Override] Infrastructure Lifecycle
# Reason: Deletion protection is intentionally disabled to facilitate seamless `terraform destroy` for the ephemeral demo environment.
AWS-0177

# [FinOps] Cost Optimization
# Reason: Performance Insights and Control Plane Logging (API, Audit, etc.) are disabled to minimize unnecessary AWS CloudWatch billing charges for the non-production environment.
AWS-0133
AWS-0038